{"tid":1952630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大越發現中意人真係一件好好好難嘅事","createTime":"2020-03-31T17:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T20:46:29.000Z","uid":316255,"like":63,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a6bc65958a4ede23aa76d33106c797e5dbe84154","tid":1952630,"uid":316255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"就算條件真係幾高質<br />\n但總係冇左<br />\n細個嗰陣中意人嘅<br />\n嗰種心動嘅感覺<br />\n更多嘅似係只係大家相處得夾<br />\n一齊得舒服開心<br />\n但心入面知道<br />\n就算佢有一日消失咗<br />\n我都唔會話move on唔到<br />\n搵過一個陪我就可以了<br />\n冇一種我非佢不可嘅戀愛臭酸味<br />\n點算<br />\n會唔會一世都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7059957996a5396d165b5ea612cac8cbfcf3c9","tid":1952630,"uid":294737,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"人大咗要求越高，睇嘅嘢越多係會有轉變<br />\n人每一刻都係度變，只係睇變好定變差啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c475c4d92bc1b2d0e151c46c2089f9038501cedb","tid":1952630,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"算啦 愛莫能助"},{"pid":"099f944c05b33583a044e7d7ebb741a81df25aa8","tid":1952630,"uid":316255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c475c4d92bc1b2d0e151c46c2089f9038501cedb","tid":1952630,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"算啦 愛莫能助"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:41:51.000Z","msg":"渣架架架"},{"pid":"e691165862e1f6679274519c5331885b1bd70662","tid":1952630,"uid":316255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a7059957996a5396d165b5ea612cac8cbfcf3c9","tid":1952630,"uid":294737,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"人大咗要求越高，睇嘅嘢越多係會有轉變<br />\n人每一刻都係度變，只係睇變好定變差啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:43:43.000Z","msg":"或者可能真係睇人透左啲啲<br />\n比起以前<br />\n所以容易左睇到一段關係入面<br />\n既雜質<br />\n沉唔撚到船啊啊啊<img src=\"/ass